2002-04-11  Charles A. Cox  <cox@fritter>

  Added support for GTK+ 2.0.  Rearranged files and directories to support
  both GTK+ 1.2 and GTK+ 2.0.
	
	gtk.cl -> gtk12.cl and gtk20.cl.
	load.cl -> loadgtk12.cl and loadgtk20.cl.
	lispex/ -> lispex-gtk12/ and lispex-gtk20/.
	notes/base-c-out.c -> notes/base-c-out.c-gtk12 and
	notes/base-c-out.c-gtk20.
	
	* Makefile: enhance 'clean'.
	* cdbind.cl: import stuff from old gtk.cl.
	* eh.cl: Use XConnectionNumber(gdk_display) instead of
	event_poll_fd, which only worked for gtk 1.2.
	* makedist.cl: update.
	* readme.txt: update.
	* notes/gtk-build.txt: include gtk20 build experiences.
	* notes/notes.txt: 

